{
  "stem": "17001.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when this old man, elderly gentleman in the uniform, and he spoke perfect Hungarian, and he said that we should volunteer and so on, if you are sick.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a handful who didn't believe what the Blockalteste said, and they volunteered.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it wasn't that many volunteer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was another time when there was this other German female officer, and they came and they selected all the young looking girls.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they said that they going to form a barrack that all the children will be.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that time, I didn't mind.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I let my children-- I let my sister Elizabeth to be selected.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they put them in the block 20-- I mean the barrack 22.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And one morning, I see that the German officer and is marching them to the end of the lager.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as I'm watching, she was making them do exercise.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Up and down and this and this and this and this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I said, I give out that little fat what he has-- what she has on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She going to lose it because how long can she-- can you keep on exercising without food and without all that?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So next day, I said to her as they were marching back, I hollered at her.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I said after Zahlappell, come to block so-and-so.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because to tell you the honest things that what happened is that somehow I had a feeling when they coming to select, and I would go over to another block to-- to stay at Zahlappell.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So what happened is that after every morning, we would stand Zahlappell in a-- a-- a different barrack, different block.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I told my sister where to come, and then she came.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
